hopobject.body: Where did you go to university? where can i buy rogaine in india How do I get your email? I looked and nothing is there. Are you sure you sent it, or did you just say that for others to see? I don't know why you are so upset. All I asked was, why is it when Christians are assaulted, you guys get flaming mad, but when others are(race, religion, sexuality, etc) you don't care? That is what made you so mad. The fact that you are a hypocrite.
